content:
2010 is the year of formation of Fen Research.


 * 14 May - https://fenresearch.com/ was registered.
 * 14 May - https://fenforge.com/ was registered. (Sometime later the url was redirected to fenresearch.com)
 * 16 June - Fen Research Ltd. was incorporated as a private company.
 * 7 September - Fen Research was founded.
